'''Thiago Alves Araujo''' (born [[October 3]] [[1983]]) is a professional [[Brazil|Brazilian]] [[mixed martial arts]] fighter.  Alves, who started training in Muay Thai when he was 15 and mixed martial arts at 17, is a Brazilian Muay Thai champion with a purple belt in [[Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu]].<ref>{{cite web
|url= http://www.sherdog.com/news/articles.asp?n_id=4854&my_page=6
|title= Sherdog.com Preview: Ultimate Fight Night 5 Part I
